reviews.text: Good place to eat breakfast
I had afternoon tea meal including roasted duck noodle and ice red bean drink. The price was reasonable and the quality of food was quite good.

Okay. Thanks to cafe de coral central branch, nature`s VERY urgent call was answered, not like toys r us in nexxus building which lock up all its toilets in the 1st and 2nd flrs...  
Bout the food, all my past orders are tasty and affordable esp. w/ free drinks or soup.
Value for money menu items, cleanliness, taste and staff are generally better than most other fast food restaurants.
So so. I ate there for breakfast and it was super busy. Eat and run. Good for business men but not for travellers. This is cdc in harbour view hk.
